channel.description:
[center][b]New Project Based In Java technology Project + Saint +[/b][/center] [center][i]Some May See I Am New To This Forums But i Know alot About Java as It Is And I Will Be Making A New Server Auto Of Java I Will Be Relesing It hopfully In About 3 months time! It Will be A Starter Source With Full everything :D This Is Actually Going to Happen so Just Because Im "New" Dont Think i Dont Know Java I Will Be Putting some Of My "Codes" In This Topic And Hopfully Some Will Think Of Using For They'r Own server![/i][/center] [center][b]Suggestions[/b][/center] [center]
I Suggest: Would You Like To Join Forums: Would You Help in This Server: Will You Be Loyal: Will You Add My MSN:
[/center] [center][i]Thanks For Reading My thread And I Am Getting To Work On This ASAP! [size=5pt]join my forums! pm me now![/size] If you Want to Contact me please Add My Msn On javaproject@hotmail.co.uk thanks + Saint +[/i][/center] [center][b]Suggestions[/b] [quote="s p i d a z"]I Suggest: Fully working range and prayers :) for jad for firecape Would You Like To Join Forums: Sure :) Would You Help in This Server: yeah I wanna join a team and help :) Will You Be Loyal: of course Will You Add My MSN: Sure[/quote] [quote="andynerd"]I Suggest: if you work on a client to run it then you could make custom spells/items/npc's/or prayer ! but server side just make it so you can use tut island :P in so many servers you have to stay as some girl or as a guy wearing iron Would You Like To Join Forums: Sure!! i can mod/ work on them 2! Would You Help in This Server: yup^_^ sounds very cool! Will You Be Loyal: of course Will You Add My MSN: yup your client needs work not to be rude ever think of using maybe icerealm and modding it? you can still give them credit so it isn't leeching just modding ;D :| You should add god mode so admins float like ghosts :D or "gods" i guess :P and make a working spell for admins/mods that sends the bad people to a jail! [/quote][/center] [center][/center] [center][b]Updates[/b][/center] [center][i]Project Elleka has Been Kind Enough To Give Me they'r client To Use! Special Thanks To Zilchuary Who Sadly Left these Forums :([/i][/center] [center][b]New GUI System Made 100% By Me![/b] [i]I Have Currently Made A New GUI For The Server It Will Have Latest News And Selection Buttons To Controll the Server Buttons Will Include: Updates Run server Compile Server Delete Character files (Y/N Option) Flood Lagg [/i] [b]GUI Picture[/b] [img]http://i193.photobucket.com/albums/z147/ownerhami/GUI.jpg[/img][/center]
